==拍攝==
電影於2014年10月27日正式在[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]的[[匹兹堡|匹兹堡]]開拍，並在1月於同一地點製作<ref>{{cite news|title=Will Smith spotted preparing for his next role in Lodi, CA|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/09/16/will-smith-spotted-preparing-for-his-next-role-in-lodi-ca/#more-57315|accessdate=2014-10-12|publisher=onlocationvacations.com|date=2014-09-16}}</ref>。11月3日至4日，拍攝於匹茲堡的一所{{link-en|丘區|Hill District}}教堂<ref>{{cite news|title=Will Smith’s ‘Game Brain’ Casting Call for a Church Scene in Pittsburgh|url=http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/will-smiths-game-brain-casting-call-for-a-church-scene-in-pittsburgh/|accessdate=2014-11-01|publisher=projectcasting.com|date=2014-10-29}}</ref>。2014年12月的第一個星期，在{{link-en|布拉多克卡內基自由圖書館|Carnegie Free Library of Braddock}}<ref>{{cite news|title=The Will Smith crew filmed at Braddock Carnegie Library this week|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2014/12/04/The-Will-Smith-film-continued-production-at-Braddock-Carnegie-Library-this-week/stories/201412040306|accessdate=2015-09-08|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712084116/http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2014/12/04/The-Will-Smith-film-continued-production-at-Braddock-Carnegie-Library-this-week/stories/201412040306|dead-url=no}}</ref>和{{link-en|匹茲堡市中心|Downtown Pittsburgh}}進行取景拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title=Will Smith’s ‘Concussion’ movie filming on location in Pittsburgh this weekend|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/12/05/will-smiths-concussion-movie-filming-on-location-in-pittsburgh-this-weekend/|accessdate=2014-12-06|publisher=onlocationvacations.com|date=2014-12-05}}</ref><ref name="Vancheri">{{cite web|first=Barbara|last=Vancheri|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2014/10/31/Will-Smith-movie-shooting-around-town/stories/201410310038|title=Will Smith football movie shooting in Pittsburgh|publisher=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|date=2014-10-31|accessdate=2015-09-08|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712083943/http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/movies/2014/10/31/Will-Smith-movie-shooting-around-town/stories/201410310038|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==發行==
2016年1月27日，索尼將本片和《[[翻轉幸福|翻轉幸福]]》、《[[家有兩個爸|家有兩個爸]]》共同排於2015年[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Will Smith’s ‘Concussion’ Drama Set for Christmas Release|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/will-smiths-concussion-drama-set-for-christmas-release-1201416809/|accessdate=2015-01-28|publisher=variety.com|date=2015-01-27|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712053212/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/will-smiths-concussion-drama-set-for-christmas-release-1201416809/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首部預告片於2015年8月31日發布在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pictures|first1=Sony|title=Concussion - Official Trailer (2015) - Will Smith|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Io6hPdC41RM|accessdate=2015-08-31|publisher=variety.com|date=2015-08-31|archive-date=2015-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904021542/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Io6hPdC41RM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
《震盪效應》獲得了正面居多的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度63%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/concussion_2015/ |title=Concussion (2015) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-12-25}}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分55<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/concussion-2015 |title=Concussion (2015) |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-12-23 |archive-date=2015-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151226070029/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/concussion-2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查指出，觀眾從A+至F之間平均給了「A」的評價<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-the-force-awakens-box-office-pack-as-moviegoers-unwrap-gift-of-choice-1201672136/ |title=Box Office Sleigh Ride: ‘Star Wars’ Soaring, ‘Daddy’s’ Bringing It Home, ‘Hateful Eight’ Selling Out |work=deadline.com}}</ref>。

===票房===
本片在美國和加拿大於2015年12月25日上映，首映週末預計能從2841間戲院獲得800至1000萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-force-awakens-christmas-box-office-joy-daddys-home-concussion-point-break-1201670872/|title=‘Force Awakens’ Will Own Christmas Weekend As Five Wide Releases Join The Fray – Box Office Preview|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2015-12-21|accessdate=2015-12-23|archive-date=2016-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101023243/http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-force-awakens-christmas-box-office-joy-daddys-home-concussion-point-break-1201670872/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週從2841間戲院中獲得了1050萬美元的票房，位居當週第七。

